BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 138.0 610 Td (UNDERSTANDING CHOLESTEROL) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 40 600 m 392 600 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 580 Td (Cholesterol is a waxy substance your body needs, but too much) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 567 Td (of the wrong kind can build up in arteries and cause heart disease.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 554 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 541 Td (HDL \(High-Density Lipoprotein\) - 'GOOD' cholesterol) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 528 Td (  - Removes cholesterol from arteries) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 515 Td (  - Higher is BETTER \(aim for 60+ mg/dL\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 502 Td (  - Raised by: exercise, healthy fats, not smoking) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 489 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 476 Td (LDL \(Low-Density Lipoprotein\) - 'BAD' cholesterol) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 463 Td (  - Deposits cholesterol IN arteries \(forms plaque\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 450 Td (  - Lower is BETTER \(aim for under 100 mg/dL\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 437 Td (  - Lowered by: diet, exercise, medications \(statins\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 424 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 411 Td (TRIGLYCERIDES - Blood fats from food) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 398 Td (  - High levels increase heart disease risk) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 385 Td (  - Aim for under 150 mg/dL) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 372 Td (  - Lowered by: reducing sugar, alcohol, refined carbs) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 359 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 346 Td (TOTAL CHOLESTEROL = HDL + LDL + \(Triglycerides / 5\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 333 Td (  - Desirable: under 200 mg/dL) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 320 Td (  - Borderline high: 200-239 mg/dL) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 307 Td (  - High: 240+ mg/dL) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 294 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 281 Td (WHY IT MATTERS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 268 Td (High cholesterol has NO SYMPTOMS until a heart attack or stroke.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 255 Td (The ONLY way to know your numbers is through a blood test.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 242 Td (Regular monitoring helps you catch changes early.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
